{"tid":1531304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（國際攻勢二連發）908《人權及民主法案》大遊行、915 BNO平權大遊行","createTime":"2019-09-02T07:32:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-10T13:23:44.000Z","uid":196430,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"5959aaa32e7afa2c2c7d3be0d6879413871fa122","tid":1531304,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:32:11.000Z","msg":"聚所周知，我地最少都要頂到10月1同中共搞大佢，咁而家距離呢個大日子仲有短短一個月，行動唔可以停<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁909係美國國會復會日，人地咁支持我哋，908當然要大搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家已經有好多post講，相信會搞得成，係差行動細節，大家可以去以下post討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n建議9月8日百萬人大遊行，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案，宣揚攬炒精神﹗<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1510235\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1510235</a><br />\n<br />\n[全登集氣]推到民陣搞，9月8號星期日大遊行，援請通過香港人權法！<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1531140\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1531140</a><br />\n<br />\n----------------------------------------------------分隔線----------------------------------------------------------<br />\n<br />\n908有著落，不如就索性嚟個國際攻勢二連發，連續搞兩個有關國際戰線嘅行動。除咗美國，而家喺英國BNO平權問題都開始有回響。（星期六應該留畀機場）<br />\nZ<br />\n參考資料︰<br />\n金融時報：BNO爭權令英國面臨被卷入香港風波的危機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1526955\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1526955</a><br />\n<br />\n之前口外部強硬回應，都知BNO問題係另一個春袋，亦都係英國介入香港問題嘅最大公約數，就只差我哋用行動去正式將佢提上國家議程，實行將英國拖埋落水﹗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且呢個行動，仲可以connect埋班唯利是圖嘅偽中立、廢老，所以事在必行，大家說對不對？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同意請推post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6719bb08444cf894cf1668b6d1599ec58d9a094","tid":1531304,"uid":69525,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:32:35.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df507754abdc7e3c75199d3e30459d20de2c6d72","tid":1531304,"uid":89006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:32:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2768b4269fb162d5bf8b5231d94b43685cbec006","tid":1531304,"uid":129873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:33:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae77806514ea30c2328c19da6f140cb5882f9a72","tid":1531304,"uid":17812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:33:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d124e930d62d111cd59f1914b5e9896b97ddf1ea","tid":1531304,"uid":257422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:34:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9月9日美國國會復會！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">9月8日<br />\n星期日<br />\n同我出黎遊行全力支持通過<br />\n《香港民主及人權法案》！！</span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ARgCLoO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FARgCLoO.jpg&h=045fa316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住練定美國國歌到時唱！！！！<br />\nMake Hong Kong great again! </span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZykHbrV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZykHbrV.jpg&h=30a62641&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">全民發夢合唱</span> <span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國歌</span></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> <span style=\"color: gold;\">We should learn how to sing</span><br />\n <em><span style=\"color: red;\">&quot;The Star-</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">Spangled Banner&quot;</span></em><br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1528828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1528828</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家仲記唔記得手足揮美國國旗唱美國國歌唱到Trump Trump都retweet!!!!</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=ef9dc84c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fdcexaminer%2Fstatus%2F1161305213841682439%3Fs%3D09&h=72f77df1\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/dcexaminer/status/1161305213841682439?s=09</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">除咗九月八日，如果<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">十月一日</span>我地再幫支共賀一賀佢，搞到全美國都知支共國慶我地用美國國歌慶祝，你話會激到維尼幾咁高興？<br />\n<br />\n而最重要，我地之前揮動美國國旗、唱美國國歌，美國傳媒一直都理解成我地係以追求人權民主自由既普世價值而表態！！！亦係動之以情地令佢地推動 香港民主及人權法案 既方法！！！<br />\n</span> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><br />\n九月八日發夢同我一齊唱！<br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">MV with Lyrics: </span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvPKp29Luryc&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=f706a471\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vPKp29Luryc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">歌詞：</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5nSVsMz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5nSVsMz.png&h=279e88f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/F1sKkdk.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FF1sKkdk.gif&h=5c4ce310&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Liberate Hong Kong, <br />\nthe Revolution of Our Times<br />\n<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"ea6113f84c561020efa0f5774a2d5fb5f4c5a270","tid":1531304,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:34:59.000Z","msg":"200萬民意做後盾，我地堅毅不屈，政府耐我地唔何！<br />\n[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a>"},{"pid":"0ab49e76c9eae744b8c2c02a7b7505ef1fe848ea","tid":1531304,"uid":287449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:35:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />借位宣傳<br />\n侵侵同d外國人都冇加你fb同ig，點知你想要咩啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好再係facebook同ig自己圍爐打飛機啦，一齊黎開始國際戰線！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個tweet幾秒鐘，一蚊都唔洗，又唔洗綁電話，安全又快捷，快d一齊轉用twitter啦<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">twitter文宣共識TG： </span></strong><a href=\"https://t.me/twittermansyunzou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ftwittermansyunzou&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=44290f8b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/twittermansyunzou</a><br />\n內有twitter詳細教學，開個account唔洗3分鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n英文唔好驚比人笑？唔洗驚，國際文宣谷幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n🔥反送中 文宣谷link🔥<br />\n國際 Channel ：<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=TzvjPMdTsSggZCZjY4uR25ugP7yqsTcUQnBN8ZzcBqk%3D&h=5de9d537\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a>"},{"pid":"1dda4f245b242a3fb7503562c0016cddfc315422","tid":1531304,"uid":196430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T07:39:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e7cc1e26b7f208e0c6c6414c4fe565316879cec","tid":1531304,"uid":122994,"like":0,"di